de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mkcop

Class MkCoPLeafEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.MTreeLeafEntry
      • de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.index.tree.metrical.mtreevariants.mktrees.mkcop.MkCoPLeafEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Entry, LeafEntry, MkCoPEntry, MTreeEntry, java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable

    class MkCoPLeafEntry
extends MTreeLeafEntry
implements MkCoPEntry
    Represents an entry in a leaf node of a MkCoP-Tree. Additionally to an MTreeLeafEntry an MkCoPLeafEntry holds the conservative and progressive approximation of its knn-distances.
    Since:
    0.1
    Author:
    Elke Achtert
